<h1>Density Calculator</h1>

<p>A simple reference tool for calculating development density.</p>

<h2>Formula</h2>
<p><strong>Density = Units ÷ Site Area (ha)</strong></p>

<h2>Example</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Site area: 0.5 ha</li>
    <li>Units: 25</li>
    <li>Density: 50 u/ha</li>
</ul>

<p>This tool supports early‑stage feasibility and massing studies.</p>
